edu.ucla.wise.commons

Class SurveyorApplication

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucla.wise.commons.WISEApplication
      • edu.ucla.wise.commons.SurveyorApplication

  • public class SurveyorApplication
extends WISEApplication
    Class to represent common elements for *this* local installation of the wise surveyor java application NOT the possibly-remote surveyor information for a given StudySpace. Never instantiated; just initialize static variables.
